Class JTextComponentNotEmptyChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pumaray.lib.gui.inputverifiers.JTextComponentNotEmptyChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, DocumentListener
    public class JTextComponentNotEmptyChecker
extends Object
implements DocumentListener
    Class that create a not empty verfier that will check that every JTextComponent that register itself with this class does not contain an empty String
